* {{ill|Tōkyū Corporation|ja|東急電鉄|12=draft}}: {{ill|Tōkyū Tōyoko Line|ja|東急東横線|12=draft}}, {{ill|Tōkyū Den-en-toshi Line|ja|東急田園都市線|12=draft}}
* {{ill|Keiō Corporation|ja|京王電鉄|12=draft}}: {{ill|Keiō Inokashira Line|ja|井の頭線|12=draft}}
* {{ill|Tokyo Metro|ja|東京メトロ|12=draft}}: {{ill|Ginza Line|ja|東京メトロ銀座線|12=draft}}, {{ill|Hanzōmon Line|ja|東京メトロ半蔵門線|12=draft}}, {{ill|Fukutoshin Line|ja|東京メトロ副都心線|12=draft}}

