* {{ill|Keiō Corporation|ja|京王電鉄|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keiō Corporation|qq=}}: {{ill|Keiō Inokashira Line|ja|井の頭線|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keiō Inokashira Line|qq=}}
